### Cabinet Dr Sonia Zouid — API tests
### Install the "REST Client" VS Code extension (humao.rest-client),
### then click "Send Request" above each block below.
### Start the server first:  npm run dev
### Create the admin first:   node scripts/createAdmin.js

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### 1) Health check → 200 { status: "OK" }
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health

### ─── PUBLIC form endpoints ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### 2) Create an appointment (valid) → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Amine Ben Ali",
  "phone": "20123456",
  "email": "amine.benali@example.tn",
  "motif": "Dépistage glaucome",
  "preferredDate": "2026-07-15",
  "preferredTime": "10:00",
  "message": "Je préfère une consultation en matinée."
}

### 3) Invalid appointment (bad phone + bad motif) → 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments
Content-Type: application/json

{ "fullName": "X", "phone": "12", "motif": "Inexistant", "preferredDate": "" }

### 4) Create a contact message (valid) → 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Sonia Gharbi",
  "email": "sonia.gharbi@example.tn",
  "phone": "22334455",
  "message": "Bonjour, quels sont vos horaires le samedi ?"
}

### ─── ADMIN: log in first (creds come from .env) ────────────────────────

# @name login
### 5) Login → 200 { token, admin }
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ "email": "admin@drzouid.tn", "password": "ChangeMe123!" }

### The token from the login response is reused below:
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### 6) Who am I → 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7) List appointments (admin) → 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7b) List appointments WITHOUT token → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments

### 8) Update an appointment status → 200  (paste a real id)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/PUT_AN_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{ "status": "done" }

### 9) Delete an appointment → 200  (paste a real id)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/appointments/PUT_AN_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10) List messages (admin) → 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/contact
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11) Delete a message → 200  (paste a real id)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/contact/PUT_AN_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
